<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="conservative-adj">conservative <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kən'sɜːvətɪv/    美 /kən'sɜːrvətɪv/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>保守的；守旧的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People are naturally conservative and do not like change. 
人天性保守，不喜欢改变。</p><footer>2014 安徽</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(预测等) 保守的；慎重的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make <strong>a conservative estimate</strong> / <strong>guess at</strong>
对…作保守估计</p></div></div>